ActCanada Not-for-profit Corporations Act
National Research Council Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Incorporation of a Corporation under the Canada Not-for-profit Corporations Act
PrecisOrder authorizing the National Research Council of Canada to (1) PROCURE THE INCORPORATION of a corporation to operate its BIOLOGICS MANUFACTURING CENTRE; and (2) acquire a membership in that corporation.
